  "description": "You can create blocks from photo easily!",
  "readme_markdown": "<h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-imageconverter\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#imageconverter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>ImageConverter</h1>\n<p><strong>You can create blocks from photo easily!</strong></p>\n<h3>\n<a id=\"user-content-feature\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#feature\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Feature</h3>\n<p>Please see this converted photo in 'Example' folder</p>\n<h3>\n<a id=\"user-content-how-to-use\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#how-to-use\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>How to use</h3>\n<p>Install this plugin and run your server. It will be created 'ImageConverter' folder in plugin folder.\nThrow photo what you want to convert to that folder. And type command <code>/convert</code></p>\n<h3>\n<a id=\"user-content-available-commands\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#available-commands\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>AVAILABLE COMMANDS</h3>\n<p><code>/convert</code> - Show conversion menu</p>\n<p><strong>Enjoy converting block XD</strong></p>\n<script defer src=\"https://static.cloudflareinsights.com/beacon.min.js/v8c78df7c7c0f484497ecbca7046644da1771523124516\" integrity=\"sha512-8DS7rgIrAmghBFwoOTujcf6D9rXvH8xm8JQ1Ja01h9QX8EzXldiszufYa4IFfKdLUKTTrnSFXLDkUEOTrZQ8Qg==\" data-cf-beacon='{\"version\":\"2024.11.0\",\"token\":\"508eb1d242ef46b690a0886422106e77\",\"r\":1,\"server_timing\":{\"name\":{\"cfCacheStatus\":true,\"cfEdge\":true,\"cfExtPri\":true,\"cfL4\":true,\"cfOrigin\":true,\"cfSpeedBrain\":true},\"location_startswith\":null}}' crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>",
